Reasoning: The paper discusses techniques for approaching capacity with short blocklengths and explores rate-compatible sphere-packing analysis in scenarios involving numerous retransmissions and different step sizes. These topics are closely related to information theory (cs.IT), communication systems (cs.COMM), network infrastructure (cs.NI), systems and control (cs.SY), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
